1 A SENATE RESOLUTION CONFIRMING NATHANIEL DENNY AS THE SECRETARY
2 OF THE DEPARTMENT OF INFORMATION TECHNOLOGY.
3 Be it resolved by the Senate:
4 SECTION 1. Having given due consideration to the matter, the Senate confirms
5 Nathaniel Denny as Secretary of the Department of Information Technology.
6 SECTION 2. This resolution is effective upon adoption.
